    "title": "Adhabu",
    "illustrator": " Melany Pietersen",
    "writtenby": " Adelheid Marie Bwire",
    "readby": " Lauwo George",
    "translator": " Monica Shank Lauwo, Lauwo George",
    "level": 2,
    "pages": [
        {
            "text": "Adhabu",
            "pagenum": 0,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_00.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_00.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Siku moja, mama alileta matunda mengi.",
            "pagenum": 1,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_01.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_01.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Tutakula matunda lini?” tunauliza. “Tutakula matunda leo jioni,” mama anasema.",
            "pagenum": 2,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_02.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_02.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Kaka yangu Rahim ni mlafi. Anaonja onja matunda yote. Anakula matunda mengi.",
            "pagenum": 3,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_03.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_03.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Angalia Rahim alichokifanya!” mdogo wangu analalamika kwa sauti. “Rahim ni mtundu na mchoyo,” ninasema.",
            "pagenum": 4,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_04.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_04.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mama amekasirishwa na Rahim.",
            "pagenum": 5,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_05.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_05.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Sisi pia tumekasirishwa na Rahim. Lakini Rahim haombi msamaha.",
            "pagenum": 6,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_06.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_06.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Hutamwadhibu Rahim?” mdogo wangu anauliza.",
            "pagenum": 7,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_07.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_07.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Rahim, muda si mrefu utajuta,” mama anaonya.",
            "pagenum": 8,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_08.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_08.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Rahim anaanza kuhisi kuumwa.",
            "pagenum": 9,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_09.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_09.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Tumbo langu linauma sana,” Rahim ananong’ona.",
            "pagenum": 10,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_10.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_10.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mama alijua hili litatokea. Matunda yanamwadhibu Rahim!",
            "pagenum": 11,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_11.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_11.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Baadaye, Rahim anatuomba msamaha. “Kamwe sitakuwa mlafi tena,” anaahidi. Na sote tunamwamini.",
            "pagenum": 12,
            "imageSrc": "./images/0342/0342_12.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "./audio/sw/0342/0342_sw_12.mp3"
        }
    ]
}